"{\n  \"text\": \"Hey everybody, Scotty here, and this is my right-hand man Mario. He's going to show you how we put on our tamper-proof seals and our labels. Um, you know, I've been watching a lot of videos lately that are advertising some sort of a magic elixir or pill for gut health. And truthfully, I just want to say, my opinion, those things aren't really the secret to gut health. Gut health is about eating good foods. It's about a good diet, low in sugars, high in raw fruits and vegetables and fermented foods like this, but it's also about living a stress-free life or as stress-free as you can in modern world, about getting enough sleep. Overall, gut health is is about overall health. You can't have a healthy gut if you're always stressed out and you're eating bad food. And that's just a matter of it. No pill or elixir is ever going to save you from this. This is something that's a lifestyle choice. Your gut is all about your life. And so you need to eat well and live well. That's how you get a good gut. Of course, fermented foods are a big part of it. But anyway, here's the final product. That's what it all looks like. Thanks, y'all.\",\n  \"sentences\": [\n    {\n      \"text\": \" Hey everybody, Scotty here, and this is my right-hand man Mario.\",\n      \"start\": 0.24,\n      \"end\": 3.76,\n      \"duration\": 3.52,\n      \"confidence\": 0.985,\n      \"tokens\": [\n        {\n          \"text\": \" He\",\n          \"start\": 0.24,\n          \"end\": 0.4,\n          \"duration\": 0.16,\n          \"confidence\": 0.994\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \"y\",\n          \"start\": 0.4,\n          \"end\": 0.48,\n          \"duration\": 0.08,\n          \"confidence\": 0.999\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \" ever\",\n          \"start\": 0.56,\n          \"end\": 0.64,\n          \"duration\": 0.08,\n          \"confidence\": 1.0\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \"yb\",\n          \"start\": 0.64,\n          \"end\": 0.